title: 'Nighttime prohibition': Warsaw city center bans alcohol sales at night
subhed: Nearly 180 municipalities in Poland have already opted to ban the sale of alcohol at night. On November 1, two central districts in Warsaw followed suit. The measure, which was initially intended to apply across the entire capital, has sparked heated debate.

title: In New York, Chanel embraces Matthieu Blazy's flair for fantasy
subhed: On December 2, the artistic director of the iconic Paris fashion house staged his first métiers d'art show in a Manhattan subway station. The hypnotic performance featured everything from voluminous dresses and pinstriped suits to fisherman sweaters.
